snippet.title: Green Day: Rock Band - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Check out a sample of what to expect from the forthcoming Green Day: Rock Band game, coming out for the Xbox 360, PS3, and Nintendo Wii on June 8th, 2010.  Note: This video is not mine, and is property of Viacom, MTV Games, and Harmonix.
